description: Outline planning permission for the comprehensive redevelopment of the land known as Webbs Industrial Estate to comprise a mixed use scheme including the demolition of existing buildings and associated structures, the alteration of the highways, engineering and construction of new buildings and structures to provide an indicative total of 26,850 sq.m (excluding basement) comprising Artisan workshops (Use Class B1), retail (Use Class A1/A2/A3), 235 residential dwellings (Use Class C3), an energy centre, creation of 143 basement and grade car parking spaces, landscaping, creation new public realm and associated works.
